com.sun.mdm.index.query
Class QualifiedField

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.mdm.index.query.QualifiedField
class QualifiedField
extends java.lang.Object

This class splits a fully qualified name into Object name and field name. So a fqfn Enterprise.SystemSBR.Person.firstName is split into object: Enterprise.SystemSBR.Person field: firstName
